01:02:08.730 --> 01:02:11.530
I need to go there quickly.

01:02:11.530 --> 01:02:13.150
I'll see you at home.

01:02:13.150 --> 01:02:14.790
Wait.

01:02:29.330 --> 01:02:31.230
Honey,

01:02:31.230 --> 01:02:33.280
